23921567-aad3-47e4-9f07-e8f3cfaae401.do_description: To make the output, you have to...make identical grid. push the color piece down 1x. Make a line of yellow above the color piece. Skip the line to the right and left and repeat only yellow lines on every other space.
23921567-aad3-47e4-9f07-e8f3cfaae401.grid_description: The output grid size...grid size is identical
23921567-aad3-47e4-9f07-e8f3cfaae401.see_description: In the input, you should see...Grid size stay the same instead with yellow.

2b9f60eb-8ec8-4f94-a1f2-1f3bfff276e4.do_description: To make the output, you have to...need to fill the yellow color boxes above the given box. like the following pattern Y-0-Y-0-Y ( 0 refer- background color, Y - yellow) don't fill the yellow box below and side(both) of the given color box.
2b9f60eb-8ec8-4f94-a1f2-1f3bfff276e4.grid_description: The output grid size...Same grid size
2b9f60eb-8ec8-4f94-a1f2-1f3bfff276e4.see_description: In the input, you should see...a single color box

b2eed25b-c798-4f51-af53-75bd1e79c7a3.do_description: To make the output, you have to...move the square that's not yellow down one space. Then create a yellow line above the square to the top of the grid. Next, leave a black column on both sides of the yellow. Then, make identical yellow columns using this pattern.
b2eed25b-c798-4f51-af53-75bd1e79c7a3.grid_description: The output grid size...stays the same
b2eed25b-c798-4f51-af53-75bd1e79c7a3.see_description: In the input, you should see...one square that's not yellow

d8540c77-8245-43ea-9a77-49d067f0bf82.do_description: To make the output, you have to...Copy the grid over. Move the colored square down once on the grid to the square below it. Make a line of yellow squares on top of the the colored square or squares (depending on how big your grid is) you just shifted down all the way to the top of the grid.
d8540c77-8245-43ea-9a77-49d067f0bf82.grid_description: The output grid size...stays the same.
d8540c77-8245-43ea-9a77-49d067f0bf82.see_description: In the input, you should see...One colored square on a black grid.
